Name: [Ally] Resonaboo
Desc:
All squad members' <color=#FE437E>Ether DMG</color> increases by <color=#2BAD00>15%</color>.
Active Skill: Summons an Ether black hole that continuously pulls in enemies, dealing <color=#FE437E>Ether DMG</color> to enemies struck and accumulating <color=#FE437E>Ether Anomaly Buildup</color>.
Desc2: Small but functional, it's a great help to Proxies in the Hollows.
